Class DOMScenarioFactory

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Builder, Composable, Configurable, ScenarioFactory
public class DOMScenarioFactory
extends AbstractScenarioFactory
implements Builder

Factory to create a default scenario from a DOM subtree. Expected format: "opName;param1;param2;..."/>. There can be 0, 1 or more params separated by ";" (default params delimiter). Comments and token delimiter can be set via setXYDelimiter methods.

Author:
Konstantin Pussep
